<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #2ecc71; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
    .receipt { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Payment Successful!</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{studentName}},</p>
      <p>Your payment for the course <strong>{{courseSubject}}</strong> has been processed successfully.</p>
      
      <div class="receipt">
        <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> ${{amount}}</p>
        <p><strong>Tutor:</strong> {{tutorName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{transactionId}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>Full chat capabilities, including file and image sharing, are now enabled for this course. Happy learning!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for using TutorFinder!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
